description:
Because he lives, I can face tomorrow. Singing with friends and family is one of the best ways to remember why life is worth living. In this gospel karaoke video, I'll invite you to join me and our friends in a fun and memorable singing experience.
Whether you're a first-time singer or a seasoned pro, this karaoke video is a great way to celebrate life and have some fun! Together, we'll belt out some of our favorite gospel songs and have a lots of laughs along the way!

Music performed by John Lalthangfala, Monalisa studio
